headline: Encompass Health (EHC) Q2 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: Encompass Health (EHC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +16.67% and +2.29%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
